  "title": "LaVar Ball Seen for First Time with Son LaMelo After Having His Foot Amputated",
  "text": "LaVar Ball made headlines earlier this week after it was revealed that he had his foot amputated following a \"serious medical issue.\"\nDetails surrounding LaVar's medical condition are currently unknown, but the outspoken sports figure seemed to be in good spirits as he posed for a photo with his son, LaMelo. The Charlotte Hornets superstar shared a photo of him and his father on his Instagram Stories on Thursday (February 20).\nLaMelo captioned the post, \"Seen my dawg b4 da game it was only right I love u pops 5L and after.\"\n57-year-old LaVar has yet to release an official statement after his surgery, but you can check out the photo in full above.\nSource: Instagram",
